And after 10 hours in the newborns there was a total atrophy of the instincts.
The chicks did not react to light or sound.
And the misfortune was that after four days they simply died.
"And twice we got the chicks to be born, but then we left it because it was impossible to work there with them," says Vladimir Sychev about the failure of the experiment with the chicks in space.
