To equipment for the educational center without barriers Studeo, which we have completed for the sixth consecutive year with the civil association Tap in Jedli<0xC4><0x8D>k<0xC5><0xAF>v <0xC3><0xBA>stav.
The students of the Jedli<0xC4><0x8D>k<0xC5><0xAF>v <0xC3><0xBA>stav school are regularly visited by teachers with whom they carry out fun and interesting activities.
