In London and Madrid it is very normal for people with a serious disability to travel on their own in public and to go to the service, to the museum, wherever they want...
But it is not very common for a large number of people with disabilities to actively participate in social life, in this regard, with The Tap Tap let’s go a little ahead!
A respectful or barrier-free society is one thing, but when the time comes for eminent athletes, artists, actors, politicians, or lawyers to emerge, it will begin to really change everything.
